#~ msgid "**Q1: Does CPU binding work on x86_64?**"
#~ msgstr "**问1：CPU 绑定在 x86_64 上有效吗？**"

#~ msgid "**Q2: Why are only the current rank’s IRQs bound?**"
#~ msgstr "**问2：为什么只绑定当前 rank 的中断？**"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To avoid multiple processes overwriting "
#~ "IRQ affinity settings for the same "
#~ "device."
#~ msgstr "避免多个进程覆盖同一设备的中断亲和性设置。"

#~ msgid "**Q3: What if my cpuset already limits CPUs?**"
