#~ msgstr ""
#~ "绑定器使用 `/proc/self/status` 中的 Cpus_allowed_list "
#~ "作为唯一合格的 CPU 集合。请确保该列表足够大。"

#~ msgid "**Q4: Does CPU binding change model outputs?**"
#~ msgstr "**问4：CPU 绑定会改变模型输出吗？**"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "No. It only affects host‑side affinity"
#~ " and should not change numerical "
#~ "results."
#~ msgstr "不会。它只影响主机侧亲和性，不应改变数值结果。"

#~ msgid "Summary"
#~ msgstr "总结"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Core Objective**: Reduce cross‑NUMA "
#~ "communication by pinning vLLM processes "
#~ "and threads to specific CPU cores, "
#~ "thereby stabilizing inference latency in "
#~ "Ascend NPU deployments (only applicable "
#~ "to ARM architectures)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**核心目标**：通过将 vLLM 进程和线程固定到特定 CPU 核心来减少跨 "
#~ "NUMA 通信，从而稳定昇腾 NPU 部署中的推理延迟（仅适用于 ARM "
#~ "架构）。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Usage**: Enable or disable with "
#~ "`enable_cpu_binding` via `additional_config` in "
#~ "both online and offline workflows."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**使用方法**：在在线和离线工作流中，通过 `additional_config` 使用 "
#~ "`enable_cpu_binding` 启用或禁用。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Key Limitations**: ARM‑only; relies on "
#~ "symmetric NUMA layouts; binding fails if"
#~ " the CPU pool has fewer than 5 "
#~ "cores; binding errors trigger a "
#~ "warning log but do not terminate "
#~ "the process."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**主要限制**：仅限 ARM 架构；依赖对称 NUMA 布局；如果 CPU"
#~ " 池少于 5 个核心，绑定失败；绑定错误会触发警告日志，但不会终止进程。"

#~ msgid "Fewer than 5 CPUs are available per logical NPU."
#~ msgstr "每个逻辑 NPU 可用的 CPU 少于 5 个。"
